description: The image shows a presentation slide titled "FROM STARTUP TO SCALE: HOW WINNING MARKETING TEAMS & STRATEGIES EVOLVE" under the title "MAU VEGAS". Four headshots of speakers or panelists are displayed below the title. The first is Michal Bubernik, Head of Marketing at Pixel Federation. Next is Margarita Vasilevski, Vice President of Performance Marketing at Scopely. The third is Sam McLellan, Chief Marketing Officer at BigBrain Games. The last is Jeet Niyogi, CMO at Fliff. Each headshot is framed with a black and white geometric design.
